                <head>Notes</head>
                <p>
                    <note id="n1" place="end" n="1">
                        <seg type="note-symbol">1</seg>
                        <p> <hi rend="italic">The Oxford English Dictionary</hi> describes a melodeon
                            as "a wind instrument, furnished with a keyboard, the bellows being
                            moved by means of pedals worked by the feet of the performer; an earlier
                            form of the 'American organ'."</p>
